item.title: About
item.description: Who I Am, Currently I’m a Software Engineer. I’m also an Electrical Engineer that tried different careers over 6 years before finding the one I am passionate about. Now I’m just grateful, focused on improving my skills and willing to help others with my experience. I love teaching and I’ve already worked as one for a few years. I’m a routine addicted. Waking up early, eating healthy, coding, going to gym, sleeping early and well, that’s my definition of a perfect day.
